text.english: Teorema: \(\texttt{sumList}\) of the pre-visit of a tree (\(\texttt{visit2}\)) is equal to \(\texttt{sumBT}\) of the tree, i.e. \[ \forall t \in BT_\mathbb{N} . \; \texttt{sumList}(\texttt{visit2}(t)) = \texttt{sumBT}(t) \]
text.italiano: Teorema: \(\texttt{sumList}\) della visita anticipa (\(\texttt{visit2}\)) di un albero Ã¨ equivalente a \(\texttt{sumBT}\) dell'albero, i.e. \[ \forall t \in BT_\mathbb{N} . \; \texttt{sumList}(\texttt{visit2}(t)) = \texttt{sumBT}(t) \]

theorem.coq: Theorem sumList_sumBT: forall t : btn , sumList (visit2 t) = sumBT t.
